@startuml
title Fabric Gateway - API Gateway Request Processing Control Flow

actor User
participant "Kubernetes API" as K8s
participant "Fabric Gateway\nOperator" as Operator
participant "GatewayWebhookRoutes" as Webhook
participant "IngressDerivationChain" as DerivationChain
participant "StackSetOperations" as StackSet
participant "Skipper\nAPI Gateway" as Skipper
participant "Authentication\n(IAM Service)" as IAM
participant "Backend Service" as Backend

== Gateway Configuration Phase ==

User -> K8s: Create/Update FabricGateway CRD
activate K8s

K8s -> Webhook: Validation Webhook Request
activate Webhook
Webhook -> Webhook: Validate FabricGateway Resource
alt Invalid Resource
    Webhook --> K8s: Reject (Validation Error)
    K8s --> User: Resource Rejected
else Valid Resource
    Webhook --> K8s: Accept
    deactivate Webhook

    K8s -> Operator: Synchronization Webhook Request
    activate Operator

    Operator -> DerivationChain: Derive Ingress from FabricGateway
    activate DerivationChain

    DerivationChain -> DerivationChain: Apply Authentication Policy
    DerivationChain -> DerivationChain: Apply Authorization Policy
    DerivationChain -> DerivationChain: Apply Rate Limiting Policy
    DerivationChain -> DerivationChain: Apply CORS Policy
    DerivationChain -> DerivationChain: Generate Skipper Routes

    DerivationChain -> StackSet: Discover Backend Services
    activate StackSet
    StackSet -> K8s: Query StackSet Resources
    K8s --> StackSet: Service Endpoints
    StackSet --> DerivationChain: Service Discovery Info
    deactivate StackSet

    DerivationChain --> Operator: Derived Ingress Specification
    deactivate DerivationChain

    Operator -> K8s: Create/Update Ingress Resource\n(Zero-Downtime)
    K8s --> Operator: Ingress Created/Updated

    Operator --> K8s: Sync Complete
    deactivate Operator

    K8s --> User: FabricGateway Resource Applied
end
deactivate K8s

== Runtime Request Processing Phase ==

User -> Skipper: HTTP API Request
activate Skipper

Skipper -> Skipper: Route Matching\n(Based on Ingress Rules)

Skipper -> IAM: Authenticate Token\n(Service/Employee Token)
activate IAM
alt Invalid Token
    IAM --> Skipper: Authentication Failed
    Skipper --> User: 401 Unauthorized
else Valid Token
    IAM --> Skipper: Authentication Success + Scopes
    deactivate IAM

    Skipper -> Skipper: Authorize Request\n(Check Scopes)
    alt Insufficient Scopes
        Skipper --> User: 403 Forbidden
    else Authorized
        Skipper -> Skipper: Apply Rate Limiting
        alt Rate Limit Exceeded
            Skipper --> User: 429 Too Many Requests
        else Within Limits
            Skipper -> Skipper: Apply CORS Headers
            Skipper -> Skipper: Apply Dynamic Filters

            Skipper -> Backend: Forward Request
            activate Backend
            Backend -> Backend: Process Request
            Backend --> Skipper: Response
            deactivate Backend

            Skipper -> Skipper: Apply Response Filters
            Skipper --> User: HTTP Response
        end
    end
end
deactivate Skipper

== Service Discovery Update Phase ==

StackSet -> K8s: StackSet Resource Updated
activate K8s
K8s -> Operator: Watch Event Triggered
activate Operator

Operator -> StackSet: Detect Service Changes
activate StackSet
StackSet -> StackSet: Identify New/Updated Services
StackSet --> Operator: Updated Service Info
deactivate StackSet

Operator -> DerivationChain: Re-derive Ingress
activate DerivationChain
DerivationChain -> DerivationChain: Update Backend Endpoints
DerivationChain --> Operator: Updated Ingress Spec
deactivate DerivationChain

Operator -> K8s: Update Ingress\n(Zero-Downtime Transition)
K8s --> Operator: Update Complete
Operator --> K8s: Reconciliation Complete
deactivate Operator
deactivate K8s

@enduml
